Module com.example.bank_teller
Package com.example.bank_teller

Class AccountDatabase

java.lang.Object
com.example.bank_teller.AccountDatabase
public class AccountDatabase extends Object
Represents database all bank accounts using an array of Accounts. An account can be opened, reopened, closed, and searched for within the database. Deposits and withdrawals can be made to and from accounts, respectively. All accounts can be returned as a String as they appear in the database, or sorted by account type, or returned as a String with their monthly interest and fee listed.
Author:
Nabihah, Maryam
